<li id="cite_note-FOOTNOTEUNRWAUNHCR20073,11-15"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-FOOTNOTEUNRWAUNHCR20073,11_15-0">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><a href="#CITEREFUNRWAUNHCR2007">UNRWA &amp; UNHCR 2007</a>, p.&#160;3,11: "The vast majority of Palestinian refugees fall under the UNRWA mandate, but there is still a large number living in other countries of the region, such as the Gulf States, Egypt, Iraq or Yemen, or further afield in Australia, Europe and America."</span>
